name: FISHER (rando_codr)
description: Hello! This game is meant for the #TEAMSEAS game jam, #SEAJAM by Polymars. By time anyone sees this the jam is over, sooooo... anyway, WASD or arrow keys to move, space to dash, except there is a timer so u can't spam, and the net points towards the cursor. Try to protect the coral from the various garbage that us humans yeet into the ocean, like E-brand sodas and "definitely-not-target" bags.
